{"type":"message","id":"f4840545","parentId":"d33e45c0","timestamp":"2026-03-27T19:29:07.252Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我直接使用 exec 来执行搜索命令。根据 skills 列表，miaoda-web-search 的触发词包括\"搜索\"、\"网页搜索\"等。但我需要先找到这个skill的位置。让我直接用 curl 或其他方式来进行搜索。\n\n实际上，根据 available_skills，miaoda-web-search 的 location 是 `~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md`，不是 `~/workspace/agent/workspace/skills/`。\n\n让我直接读取正确的路径。","thinkingSignature":"d12741cdb71a7b5b3bc23363df5c702a6a36997d1f24236e548c3ced54415fab"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_e4ogyn27j0s0_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1201,"output":139,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45321,"cost":{"input":0.0003603,"output":0.0001668,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0018465299999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774639742364}}
{"type":"message","id":"07cd7a71","parentId":"f4840545","timestamp":"2026-03-27T19:29:07.258Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_e4ogyn27j0s0_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774639747255}}
{"type":"message","id":"ea7bd66a","parentId":"07cd7a71","timestamp":"2026-03-27T19:29:11.760Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我需要使用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 来搜索相关信息。让我搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等道简网络相关行业的最新动态。\n\n让我执行多个搜索：\n1. 企业数字化转型最新动态 2026\n2. 智能安防行业最新动态 2026\n3. 网络系统集成最新动态 2026\n4. IT运维服务最新动态 2026\n\n然后整合3-5条关键信息保存到学习笔记。","thinkingSignature":"f90792a620618b43deae7f0d4c57e599f1ede115604f4fc92d1fd2d5baa9d6f0"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_amm66m8tct4u_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型最新动态 2026\" 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1855,"output":165,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46001,"cost":{"input":0.0005565,"output":0.000198,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00207393}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774639747258}}
